issues.title: Thermal zone overlap errors during low-light tests
issues.description: Errors occur in safety analysis when thermal zones overlap under low-light conditions. Optimize preprocessing for boundary detection.

issues.title: Anomaly overlay misalignment in QA demos
issues.description: During QA demonstrations, anomaly overlays misalign with bounding boxes when thermal layers are active. Debug overlay logic.

commits.message: Optimized preprocessing to address thermal zone overlap errors.
Aligned anomaly overlays with bounding boxes for QA tests.

issues.title: Increased latency for real-time deepfake detection
issues.description: Latency spikes occur during peak processing in real-time deepfake detection. Profile and optimize inference pipeline.

issues.title: Model accuracy drops for synthesized audio-video pairs
issues.description: Deepfake detection shows reduced accuracy for synthesized audio-video combinations. Augment dataset and retrain models.

commits.message: Optimized inference pipeline to reduce latency spikes in real-time processing.
Augmented dataset with synthesized audio-video pairs for retraining.

issues.title: Edge case latency for nighttime suburban scenarios
issues.description: Latency spikes observed in suburban tests during nighttime pedestrian detection. Profile bottlenecks and refine the pipeline.

issues.title: False positives for crowd detection in urban settings
issues.description: Pedestrian detection model triggers false positives for crowds in dense urban areas. Refine model thresholds and training data.

commits.message: Addressed latency spikes for nighttime suburban scenarios.
Refined thresholds to reduce false positives in urban crowd detection.
